#. <section class="sutta" id="sn1.36"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.36:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.36:0.2"
msgid "4. Satullapakāyikavagga"
msgstr "4. The Satullapa Group"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.36:0.3"
msgid "36. Saddhāsutta"
msgstr "36. Faith"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.36:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn1.36:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā satullapakāyikā devatāyo abhikkantāya rattiyā "
"abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, several glorious deities of the Satullapa Group, "
"lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, and stood "
"to one side."

msgctxt "sn1.36:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Standing to one side, one deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.54"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.36:2.1"
msgid "“Saddhā dutiyā purisassa hoti,"
msgstr "“Faith is a person’s partner."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:2.2"
msgid "No ce assaddhiyaṃ avatiṭṭhati;"
msgstr "If faithlessness doesn’t linger,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:2.3"
msgid "Yaso ca kittī ca tatvassa hoti,"
msgstr "fame and renown are theirs,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:2.4"
msgid "Saggañca so gacchati sarīraṃ vihāyā”ti."
msgstr "and when they discard this corpse they go to heaven.”"

# See https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/possible-textual-loss-in-sn-1-36/3350
#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.36:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr "Then another deity recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.36:4.1"
msgid "“Kodhaṃ jahe vippajaheyya mānaṃ,"
msgstr "“You should give up anger and get rid of conceit,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:4.2"
msgid "Saṃyojanaṃ sabbamatikkameyya;"
msgstr "and get past all the fetters."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:4.3"
msgid "Taṃ nāmarūpasmimasajjamānaṃ,"
msgstr "Clingings don’t torment the one who has nothing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:4.4"
msgid "Akiñcanaṃ nānupatanti saṅgā”ti."
msgstr "not clinging to name and form.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.36:5.1"
msgid "“Pamādamanuyuñjanti,"
msgstr "“Fools and unintelligent people"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:5.2"
msgid "bālā dummedhino janā;"
msgstr "devote themselves to negligence."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:5.3"
msgid "Appamādañca medhāvī,"
msgstr "But the intelligent protect diligence"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:5.4"
msgid "dhanaṃ seṭṭhaṃva rakkhati."
msgstr "as their best treasure."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.36:6.1"
msgid "Mā pamādamanuyuñjetha,"
msgstr "Don’t devote yourself to negligence,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:6.2"
msgid "mā kāmarati santhavaṃ;"
msgstr "or delight in sexual intimacy."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:6.3"
msgid "Appamatto hi jhāyanto,"
msgstr "For if you’re diligent and practice absorption,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.36:6.4"
msgid "pappoti paramaṃ sukhan”ti."
msgstr "you’ll attain the highest happiness.”"
